"{\"uid\": \"aninews.in-news-national-general-news-haryana-govt-to-honour-olympic-medallist-manu-bhaker20240728205155\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Add ANI As A Trusted Source For Reliable Information  ANI |Updated:Jul 28, 2024 20:51IST  Ambala (Haryana) [India], July 28 (ANI):HaryanaMinisterAseem Goel announced on Sunday that theHaryanaGovernmentwill honourManu Bhaker, who won the Olympicmedal\\\">bronzemedalin Shooting.Furthermore, Goel said that a scheme would be inaugurated by her in his ministry.Aseem Goel is the Minister of State of Transport, Women, and Child Development (with an independent charge) in theHaryanaGovernment.Addressing media persons,HaryanaMinisterAsim Goyalsaid, \\\"This is an achievement for all daughters of the nation.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 90, \"end\": 96, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ambala\", \"score\": 0.9999999877986739, \"rank\": 1.1668466623460026e-08, \"text\": \"Ambala\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ambala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ambala\"}, {\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.75571449181796e-13, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The whole nation is proud of the achievement ofManu Bhaker.\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When she comes back, we will honour her upon her arrival.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 717, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, if she arrives here, we will get a scheme inaugurated by her in our ministry.\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The 22-year-old became the first Indian woman to win amedalin shooting at theOlympics.Bhaker brought India's firstmedalin the ongoing mega event as she won amedal